How is Chinese-style ecological conservation different? What role are law and technology playing? How to deal with economic development at the same time? Ahimsa Campos-Arceiz, professor and principal investigator of Megafauna Ecology and Conservation Group at Xishuangbanna Tropical Botanical Garden, and Li Yuhan, team leader of Yangtze Delta Region Office at Shan Shui Conservation Center shared their experiences and what they have witnessed from different countries.